---
title: Tex-Mex Cannellini Bean & Bacon Quesadillas with Radish Salsa & Chipotle Yoghurt
description: Cannellini beans, Cheddar and carrot unite to make a hearty and delicious filling for these quesadillas. Simply spoon the cheesy filling onto the tortillas, fold them in half and bake. Easy cheesy dinner coming right up!
